sentence: what are the cities in states through which the mississippi runs ?
sentence-with-vars: what are the cities in states through which the river0 runs ?
sql: select city.city_name from city where city.state_name in ( select river.traverse from river where river.river_name = ' mississippi ' ) ;
sql-with-vars: select city.city_name from city where city.state_name in ( select river.traverse from river where river.river_name = ' river0 ' ) ;
